text: Kamal Rani Varun (3 May 1958 - 2 August 2020) was an Indian politician. She was member of Uttar Pradesh Legislative Assembly from 2017 to 2020. She was also a member of Eleventh and Twelfth Lok Sabha between 1996 and 1999. She was born in Lucknow. Varun was a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. On 2 August 2020, Varun died at a hospital in Lucknow at the age of 62 from COVID-19. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in India Category:Politicians from Lucknow Category:Members of the Lok Sabha
